{"tid":187417,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【智力報告】售兩支雙飛人藥水收5萬元 藥房店員待索智力評估報告","createTime":"2017-04-05T02:52:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T02:56:25.000Z","uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"541e5832020cc928103b0d572e212ed28705060d","tid":187417,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:52:13.000Z","msg":"六旬內地婦前年到旺角一藥坊購買兩支共值60元的法國雙飛人藥水，卻遭店員用信用卡過數5萬元。兩名年輕男店員早前經審訊後，被裁定欺詐罪成，裁判官原定今判刑，惟報告建議替其中一人索取智力評估報告，裁判官擔心或影響其求情，決定跟隨建議另索閱報告，押後判刑。<br />\n<br />\n九龍城法院暫委裁判官梁禮賢閱讀兩名被告梁家葆（20歲）及鄧子豪（23歲）的青少年罪犯評估委員會報告後，指報告建議再索取感化報告，但梁官指不會考慮，惟最終按報告建議，為梁索取教導所、為鄧索取勞教、心理及智力評估報告，兩人續還柙至本月26日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n鄧的大律師求情指他案發後沒再工作，靠母親供養，案件亦被傳媒廣泛報道，令他對母親的歉疚更大。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指兩名被告前年11月29日在旺角西洋菜南街「龍興中西藥坊」犯案。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56523485&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56523485%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170405&d=e9hI6ag5UTzhCSVhase9yBxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=5471952e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56523485%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170405&h=7b4827fc\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56523485&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170405</a>"},{"pid":"8ad5dbebedcb6496a2dc2927e6aca07eb286c58a","tid":187417,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:54:00.000Z","msg":"智力正常就判重D<br />\n弱智就判佢入小欖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655bd34fbb9f271e91b78b1c16ed230d31257f15","tid":187417,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T02:55:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14e694e9e8bbc60862ea06c4eb2b015e74c866c0","tid":187417,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"